{"tid":1028496,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個時老佛爺Karl Lagerfeld 今日於巴黎逝世，享年 85 歲","createTime":"2019-02-19T14:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T15:27:15.000Z","uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"406b1e6a36c5530834594e329709e2913e8896a6","tid":1028496,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"港台地區晚間七點半，突然接獲法國公布 Karl Lagerfeld 於今日逝世的消息，時尚大帝離開我們而去了。<br />\n<br />\n自從 Karl Lagerfeld 於上個月底缺席 Chanel 的 2019 春夏高訂大秀 (相關報導點此) 之兩場謝幕，並由工作室總監 Virginie Viard 挽著義大利模特兒 Vittoria Ceretti 代為謝幕以後，時尚圈便開始關注從不缺席大秀謝幕的 Karl Lagerfeld 怎麼會首度沒有現身。經法國雜誌 Closer 報導，Karl Lagerfeld 今日於 American Hospital of Paris 逝世，雖然近幾週 Karl Lagerfeld 確實健康狀況不佳，時尚大帝的死因目前仍然未知。<br />\n<br />\n許多名人與媒體已在社群媒體上哀悼這位時尚傳奇的離開，並透過貼文聊表對 Karl Lagerfeld 的景仰。"},{"pid":"68bcc29187eeb53cd332fcefed4a671c6822ac0d","tid":1028496,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"老佛爺駕崩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa318f9e579a765f34ceafa1a5337881ad1fc1fc","tid":1028496,"uid":44986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98800d76d1f9923c7d4592cdf86948edfdf8d5ac","tid":1028496,"uid":69994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:22:31.000Z","msg":"謝四個造型係咪學佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6a2dca578e0b9fdc2725a8337a8c25e910dfd2","tid":1028496,"uid":43804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98800d76d1f9923c7d4592cdf86948edfdf8d5ac","tid":1028496,"uid":69994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"